        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "emm `bufIsChanged` is called in multiple places, and it also affects the flag shown in the statusline. the prompt buffer is still `modifiable` see `help modifiable`. I tried using this diff patch, The test case you added also passes when using diff patch. However, the case that fails in CI also fails locally for me — but if I use diff, it passes. I’m not very familiar with the prompt buffer other opinions on this.\r\n\r\nEdit:\r\nWe are only ignoring the modified flag when closing the buffer. We should not remove the modifiable or modified indicator from the statusline. If the buffer has been modified, it is correct and expected for the statusline to show it as modified. ",
            "created_at": "2026-03-02T05:44:53Z",
